386→                        <div id="content">Let $A,B\subseteq \{1,\ldots,N\}$ be such that all the products $ab$ with $a\in A$ and $b\in B$ are distinct. Is it true that\[\lvert A\rvert \lvert B\rvert \ll \frac{N^2}{\log N}?\]</div>
387→                        <div id="problem_id"><a href="/490">#490</a>: <a href="#cite-Er61-490" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er61','490'); return false;">[Er61,p.237]</a><a href="#cite-Er69-490" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er69','490'); return false;">[Er69,p.81]</a><a href="#cite-Er72-490" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er72','490'); return false;">[Er72,p.81]</a><a href="#cite-Er73-490" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er73','490'); return false;">[Er73,p.131]</a></div>
